as primary text\n```\n\n### F4 — Docs\n\n```\ndocs/DEMO.md: steps for demo1–4 screenshots + Open Folder requirement for Source\n```\n\n---\n\n## Рекомендуемый smoke (после F1)\n\n```bash\npnpm dev\n# Open Folder → /home/resu/Documents/dev/ast-canvas\n# Expect toolbar: 📁 ast-canvas · N files · M nodes\n# Click \"3 · semantic\" → Content OK\n# Codemap → click buildSemanticMap.ts → Source shows real file\n# Regenerate (mock/haiku) optional\n```\n\n---\n\n## Одной строкой\n\nДемо **доказало**: карта monorepo + split + content/codemap **живые**; **demo4** вскрыл дыру **Source без Open Folder / resolve path**. Дальше: F1 path+toolbar, затем Phase 5 DepGraph.\n````\n</attachment>\n\n</attachments>\n<context>\nThe current date is 2026-07-09.\nTerminals:\nTerminal: bash\nTerminal: 🚀 Launch Electron + Dev Server\nLast Command: /usr/bin/env INFINITY_LLM_PROVIDER=openai-compatible INFINITY_LLM_BASE_URL=http://localhost:20128/v1 INFINITY_LLM_MODEL=kr/claude-haiku-4.5 'NODE_OPTIONS= --require /usr/share/code/resources/app/extensions/ms-vscode.js-debug/src/bootloader.js  --inspect-publish-uid=http' 'VSCODE_INSPECTOR_OPTIONS=:::{\"inspectorIpc\":\"/tmp/node-cdp.9204-75593a36-1.sock\",\"deferredMode\":false,\"waitForDebugger\":\"\",\"execPath\":\"/home/resu/.nvm/versions/node/v22.23.1/bin/node\",\"onlyEntrypoint\":false,\"autoAttachMode\":\"always\",\"fileCallback\":\"/tmp/node-debug-callback-656d4d36a9813327\"}' /home/resu/.nvm/versions/node/v22.23.1/bin/pnpm dev\nCwd: /home/resu/Documents/dev/ast-canvas\nExit Code: 0\n\n</context>\n<editorContext>\nThe user's current file is /home/resu/Documents/dev/ast-canvas/revu.md. The current selection is from line 1 to line 188.\n</editorContext>\n<reminderInstructions>\nWhen using the replace_string_in_file tool, include 3-5 lines of unchanged code before and after the string you want to replace, to make it unambiguous which part of the file should be edited.\nFor maximum efficiency, whenever you plan to perform multiple independent edit op